flavor_text_entries.diamond:
It crosses its knifelike arms in
front of its chest when it cries.
It can compose melodies ad lib.
flavor_text_entries.pearl:
It signals its emotions with its
melodies. Scientists are studying
these melodic patterns.
flavor_text_entries.platinum:
There is a village that hosts a
contest based on the amazingly
variable cries of this Pokémon.
flavor_text_entries.heartgold:
By allowing its cry to resonate in
the hollow of its belly, it produces
a captivating sound.

flavor_text_entries.legends-arceus:
It uses its cutlass-like arms to produce sound, the melody of
which varies from individual to individual. It is a worthwhile
endeavor to seek out one's favorite tunes.
